title: Episode 38 Ft. Yo Gotti
itunes:title: Episode 38 Ft. Yo Gotti
description:
Right before releasing his new album “The Art of Hustle” Yo Gotti sits down with the Ladies of Lip Service (Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Stephanie Santiago) and discusses the difference between being a fan and stalking, expectations when you fly a female in, pregnancy sex, and identifies what makes a woman grimy vs a hustler. Yo Gotti explains why he doesn’t drink and what his vices are, and then plays the dirty mind game with the ladies.
